project:
HTML element example

The content here is all shown inside a HTML Element object. This is a paragraph of text using the <p> tag. This example demonstrates several features of the HTML Element plugin, including:

  • HTML tags for styling like bold and italic
  • Formatting tags like headers, the details/summary tags, and this bullet point list
  • CSS styling (via the project file mystyles.css)
  • Using CSS animations to animate some elements
  • Including a button and detecting when it is clicked (via the element class)
